org.opcfoundation.ua.builtintypes

Class NodeId

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opcfoundation.ua.builtintypes.NodeId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<NodeId>

    public final class NodeId
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<NodeId>
    An identifier of a node in the address space of an OPC UA server. The class Id is immutable, and hash-equals-comparable with NodeIds and ExpandedNodeIds with a NamespaceIndex and no ServerIndex. If the given object is byte[] it must not be changed.

    NodeIds are equals comparable with ExpandedNodeIds that are constructed with NamespaceIndex and no ServerIndex.

    See Also:
    An identifier optional ServerIndex and/or explicit NamespaceUri, NamespaceTable
